originalSql:
SELECT 
    p.p_brand,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) AS supplier_count,
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS avg_supply_cost,
    MIN(l.l_shipdate) AS first_ship_date,
    MAX(l.l_shipdate) AS last_ship_date,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT TRIM(p.p_name), ', ') AS part_names,
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue
FROM 
    part p
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN 
    supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    lineitem l ON l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN 
    orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN 
    customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
WHERE 
    p.p_size > 20 
    AND l.l_shipmode IN ('AIR', 'RAIL')
    AND c.c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING'
GROUP BY 
    p.p_brand
ORDER BY 
    total_revenue DESC
LIMIT 10

FROM (SELECT "part"."p_brand" AS "P_BRAND", COUNT(DISTINCT "supplier"."s_suppkey") AS "SUPPLIER_COUNT", AVG("partsupp"."ps_supplycost") AS "AVG_SUPPLY_COST", MIN("lineitem"."l_shipdate") AS "FIRST_SHIP_DATE", MAX("lineitem"."l_shipdate") AS "LAST_SHIP_DATE", LISTAGG(DISTINCT TRIM(BOTH ' ' FROM "part"."p_name"), ', ') AS "PART_NAMES", SUM("lineitem"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "lineitem"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE"
FROM "part"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey"
INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "partsupp"."ps_suppkey" = "supplier"."s_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "lineitem" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "s1"."o_orderkey"
INNER JOIN "customer" ON "s1"."o_custkey" = "customer"."c_custkey"
WHERE "part"."p_size" > 20 AND ("lineitem"."l_shipmode" = 'AIR' OR "lineitem"."l_shipmode" = 'RAIL') AND "customer"."c_mktsegment" = 'BUILDING'
GROUP BY "part"."p_brand"
ORDER BY 7 DESC NULLS FIRST
LIMIT 10) AS "t3"
